{"id": "1508020197439836281", "channel_id": "1356210800091467928", "type": 0, "author_id": "451214723002793987", "author_name": "cyber_hunter", "author_bot": false, "content": "+codes", "timestamp": "2026-05-24T08:13:52.730000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1356210800091467928", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "【Newcomer Help】Forum Introduction", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956"}
{"id": "1508020198144217189", "channel_id": "1356210800091467928", "type": 0, "author_id": "204255221017214977", "author_name": "YAGPDB.xyz", "author_bot": true, "content": "All codes listed below are currently active and confirmed to be working.:\r\n- HVGX-HLDX-QKKN **`never`**\r\n- QKBQ-SSDG-JZYU  **`never`**\r\n- Catsgift  **`never`**\r\n- Dc5000  **`never`**\r\n- Silverkey  **`never`**\r\n- SayaNoUta  <t:1786895940:R>\r\n- YouSavedMorimens  <t:1787500740:R>\r\n- DFQV-XQZV-SQAY  <t:1779379140:R>\r\n- HXET-MDBW-CWPE  <t:1780156740:R>\r\n\r\nPlease check in <#1355094251775459399> or <#1355085076500578363> for new codes!", "timestamp": "2026-05-24T08:13:52.898000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1356210800091467928", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "【Newcomer Help】Forum Introduction", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956"}
{"id": "1508193284810342472", "channel_id": "1508193284810342472", "type": 0, "author_id": "145731220368654336", "author_name": "cyberse7en", "author_bot": false, "content": "I could use some perspective on who/what to pull for to further develop my account.\n\nBeen playing for 2 months, currently on Arc2Ch4 normal (no prog issues yet, just been lazy about continuing MSQ <:Helot_slack_off:1459092159465521184>) and hit 360 DTide this time around - slowly getting more comfortable with that mode.\n\nIn terms of teams I've been using for DTide:\n1. E0 Vort + Celeste + 2\n2. E2 Mouch + Thais/Aigis/Helot (so far it feels kinda rough w/o Lily's wheel and no DR substats on covs)\n3. E3 Kath + 3 (Horla's still E0 for now and Tinct also E0 WIP); can slot E0 Ryker or +2 Karen here\n4. Random bullshit go with E0 Arachne & E0 sig + assorted standard chars (Caecus or Liz or Jenkin so far)\n5. Whale borrow w/ leftovers\n\n__Current pull plan:__\n- Castor E0 + his wheel\n- At least E1 Clem next month during her regular rerun\n\nBeyond that, I'm lost on what to aim for next... <:Jenkin_think:1459079611131494543>\n\nI feel like I'm missing a 4th dedicated carry for A4 onwards (idk how often Caecus rouse solo carry is viable or how much investment is needed for that, ditto with E0 Arachne at higher HP pools)\n- ❌ Not interested in Saya, Caraboo, GTulu as far as known future characters\n- ❌ Pollux, GMurphy, Corpo all seem fun but are too investment-heavy for me right now (even if we had regular reruns for hanniversary <:please:1356053110375714817>)\n\n__Other options I'm considering:__\n- E0 Xu + her wheel; idk how helpful she'd be in general, since I'm missing Lily/Salv, GDoll only E1, and Liz is still E0 for poison\n- E1 Murphy next month after Clem to bolster my Vort team <:Murphy_satisfy:1468258389850193960> \n- Pickman had a relatively recent rerun, so I could try to get 1 copy of him and maybe his wheel on 24h banner, then E2 him eventually with protos (just a hunch but I suspect his next proper rerun won't be for a while)\n- After his recent buffs, how cope would it be to pull for Dore's wheel and 1 dupe to E1 him on 24h banner...? <:doresain_proud:1468257815238938645>", "timestamp": "2026-05-24T19:41:39.975000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1508193285309595738", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1551200, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1508193284810342472/1508193285309595738/image.png?ex=6a154eb4&is=6a13fd34&hm=91e861a9c7041ae13e4cef690bada82f35cb484b330db0881372964417979b2e&"}, {"id": "1508193285980557465", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 970752, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1508193284810342472/1508193285980557465/image.png?ex=6a154eb4&is=6a13fd34&hm=f72c7c41713c17b6d0ce476a3201e8a85000e53b8a7d74790daad5f869b93035&"}, {"id": "1508193286416760832", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2139694, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1508193284810342472/1508193286416760832/image.png?ex=6a154eb4&is=6a13fd34&hm=7c48060242f9798ef5df82999b89e31d4bcb36051120cd39e8610f0a6d151389&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1508193284810342472", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "⬅ Account Direction Advice ➡", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747463379390545", "1400747489132412979", "1400747088995811358"], "is_thread_starter": true}
